dc_title_s: Spain and France, Bay of Biscay, Brest to Cabo Finisterre (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by spot heights. "Soundings in meters." Includes index to next larger scale charts. Map no.37025 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
